title: Neutral Figures
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

During a campaign, some figures are denoted as neutral. These figures are only present in specific missions. The rules regarding these figures are described in the mission.

* No player controls a neutral figure. Neutral figures cannot activate or perform actions.
* These figures cannot suffer [img[Damage.png]] (damage) or be targeted by attacks, abilities, or any game effect except as specified by the missionâ€™s rules.
* Figures can move through spaces containing neutral figures at no additional movement point cost.
* Neutral figures block line of sight. 

